$REGN Morgan Stanley upgraded Intuit (INTU) to Overweight from Equal Weight as they believe faster EPS growth and an improving secular story set up a positive risk/reward.
Cantor Fitzgerald upgraded Regeneron Pharma (REGN) to Overweight from Neutral as they believe that investors are still underappreciating Dupixent as a growth driver in both the near and long-term. Additionally, they recognize that there is significant focus on vaccines, the holy grail for COVID-19, but firm thinks antibodies are going to be an important treatment and prevention option, as well. Firm also thinks that REGN-COV2 could be another unappreciated near-term revenue driver in 2021.
